\left(\left(\sum_{l=-2^{t - 1} + 1}^{-\left(\varepsilon + 1\right)} \left|\alpha_{l}\right|^{2}\right) + \left(\sum_{l=\varepsilon + 1}^{2^{t - 1}} \left|\alpha_{l}\right|^{2}\right)\right) \leq \left(\left(\sum_{l=-2^{t - 1} + 1}^{-\left(\varepsilon + 1\right)} \frac{1}{4 \cdot \left(l - \left(2^{t} \cdot \delta\right)\right)^{2}}\right) + \left(\sum_{l=\varepsilon + 1}^{2^{t - 1}} \frac{1}{4 \cdot \left(l - \left(2^{t} \cdot \delta\right)\right)^{2}}\right)\right)